quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  5,24,woh bolay ke moose! jab taq woh log wahan hain hum kabhi wahan nahi ja satke ( agar larna hi zaroor hai ) to tum aur tumhara khuda jao aur laro hum yahin baithy rahen ge
  5,25,moose ne ( khuda se ) iltija ki ke perwar-digaar mein apne aur apne bhai ke siwa aur kisi par ikhtiyar nahi rakhta to hum mein aur un nafarman logon mein judai kardey
  5,26,khuda ne farmaya ke woh malik un par chalees baras taq ke liye haraam kar diya gaya ( ke wahan jaane nah payen ge aur jungle ki ) zameen mein srgrdan phirtay rahen ge to un nafarman logon ke haal par afsos nah karo
  5,27,aur ( ae Mohammad ) un ko aadam ke do beton ( Habil aur Qabeel ) ke halaat ( jo bilkul ) sachey ( hain ) parh kar suna do ke jab un dono ne khuda ( ki janab mein ) kuch niazain charhayen to aik ki niaz to qubool ho gayi aur dosray ki qubool nah hui ( tab Qabeel Habil se ) kehnay laga ke mein tujhe qatal karoon ga is ne kaha ke khuda parhaiz garon hi ki ( niaz ) qubool farmaya karta hai
  5,28,aur agar to mujhe qatal karne ke liye mujh par haath chalaye ga to mein tujh ko qatal karne ke liye tujh par haath nahi chlaon ga mujhe to khuday-e rab alameen se dar lagta hai
  5,29,mein chahta hon ke to mere gunah mein bhi makhoz ho aur apne gunah mein bhi phir ( Zumra ) ahal dozakh mein ho aur zaalmon ki yahi saza hai
  5,30,magar is ke nafs ne is ko bhai ke qatal hi ki targheeb di to is ne usay qatal kar diya aur khasara uthany walon mein ho gaya
  5,31,ab khuda ne aik kowa bheja jo zameen kurednay laga taakay usay dukhaay ke apne bhai ki laash ko kionkar chupaye kehnay laga ae hai mujh se itna bhi nah ho saka ke is kaway ke barabar hota ke apne bhai ki laash chhupa deta phir woh pasheman howa
